Class SkeinParameters

Remarks

Parameterised Skein can be used for:

  • MAC generation, by providing a SetKey(Byte[]).
  • Randomised hashing, by providing a SetNonce(Byte[]).
  • A hash function for digital signatures, associating a SetPublicKey(Byte[]) with the message digest.
  • A key derivation function, by providing a SetKeyIdentifier(Byte[]).
  • Personalised hashing, by providing a SetPersonalisation(DateTime, String, String) or SetPersonalisation(Byte[]) personalisation string.
